# 📊 Indian States Growth vs Development Dashboard – Presentation

This presentation provides a complete walkthrough of the **Indian States Growth vs Development Dashboard**, developed to analyze regional disparities across India using key socio-economic indicators.

The project goes beyond traditional GDP analysis by integrating **Population, Gross State Domestic Product (GSDP), Per Capita Income, Human Development Index (HDI), Literacy Rate, Poverty, and Unemployment** to understand how economic growth translates into human development.

The presentation demonstrates the dashboard design process, analytical methodology, KPI development, SQL-based analysis, Excel dashboard creation, and key insights derived from the data. It is intended for portfolio showcasing, recruiter evaluation, academic presentations, and interview demonstrations.

---

## 🚀 Project Highlights

✔ Growth vs Development Analysis  
✔ Interactive Excel Dashboard  
✔ SQL-Based Data Analysis  
✔ KPI & Business Insights  
✔ Data Visualization & Storytelling  
✔ State-wise Comparative Analysis  
✔ Development Score Model  
✔ Growth & Divergence Index

